Research & Projects


Selected research projects in causal inference, econometrics, and time-series modeling.





&lt;div class="project-top"&gt;
  &lt;h3&gt;Rent vs Shelter Population in NYC&lt;/h3&gt;
  &lt;div class="project-tags"&gt;
